    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and will require extensive mechanical and cosmetic restoration. The engine currently runs poorly with a persistent knock, and the transmission exhibits significant slipping, suggesting a full rebuild or replacement is necessary. On the exterior, there is noticeable rust on the wheel wells and several large dents, while the interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This car is sold as-is and is recommended only for those looking for a major project or a source for parts.",
